because of scalpers?

541
00:36:31,814 --> 00:36:33,816
Starting today,
I'm reporting scalpers.

542
00:36:33,900 --> 00:36:36,027
Because of scalpers, macros,
and Goldie's ignorance,

543
00:36:36,110 --> 00:36:38,863
