TICKET SCALPERS

545
00:36:43,826 --> 00:36:47,371
Is the transfer still available?

546
00:36:49,665 --> 00:36:51,626
Yes, please make an offer.

547
00:36:53,669 --> 00:36:55,087
500,000 Won.

548
