555
00:38:44,447 --> 00:38:46,365
You have to smile, speak, and act

556
00:38:46,449 --> 00:38:48,659
exactly the way they want,

557
00:38:49,702 --> 00:38:52,955
fitting yourself to their desires.

558
00:38:53,539 --> 00:38:56,500
That's the only way to be loved.

559
00:38:58,044 --> 00:39:00,546
