562
00:39:10,806 --> 00:39:12,350
The fear that you're fading,

563
00:39:12,933 --> 00:39:15,353
disappearing entirely,

564
00:39:15,436 --> 00:39:18,147
turned into panic attacks.

565
00:39:18,773 --> 00:39:21,609
The tinnitus is also part of the symptoms.

566
00:39:23,277 --> 00:39:26,155
We need to begin treatment
before it worsens--

567
00:39:26,238 --> 00:39:27,114
Doctor,

568
00:39:28,282 --> 00:39:30,284
I already disappeared a long time ago.

569
00:39:32,495 --> 00:39:35,706
Just give me the meds, I'm busy.

570
00:39:36,665 --> 00:39:37,666
We will be ready soon.

571
00:39:39,585 --> 00:39:40,920
Ra-ik, where are you!

572
00:39:41,003 --> 00:39:43,506
